{"tid":384684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女唔係處 你心有條刺既 想唔想入黎拔走佢？","createTime":"2017-09-02T13:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T18:53:11.000Z","uid":54581,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"034b6c2a9222c53eab2f5ec4f8f25d9be9d6cc1c","tid":384684,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"你冷靜啲諗下<br />\n<br />\n佢俾人破處 好大可能係中出內射 <br />\n<br />\n因為我破女人處係一定唔帶套的 一路揸實對波一路大力啪 直到想射就頂到盡 大家有默契既就我射個下佢陰道都會收縮 啜住我jerjer<br />\n<br />\n但我唔知你女友個case係點，唔敢太肯定講<br />\n<br />\n題外話扑得野 應該口交都試過 <br />\n<br />\n不過第一次既女人多數唔識含 啲牙會刮龜頭 深喉又咳到仆街<br />\n<br />\n如果他日你條女幫你含唔會刮jerjer既<br />\n<br />\n你就諗下啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇左咁耐 <br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得無問題既，咁就唔好再諗啦 最多咪就係俾人中出口爆  好少女人會玩屎忽的放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你接受唔到 建議你飛左佢，因為總有一日你會諗起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你諗起你條女俾人扑而有扯旗既，多數係天生m底，對帶綠帽有興趣<br />\n建議你留contact俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893bce3eeec70151d6789ca5f79d07c2f0891a64","tid":384684,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c2ccf7fa5846ed509fd6c26b1ee7d37824390a","tid":384684,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1a81f55fb3ece673d7de9e78dca7077351fdfeee","tid":384684,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"73999cf42ddc430ea6e244a2bb4d4651de960645","tid":384684,"uid":132847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:49:28.000